Package: ipcw
Title: Inverse Probability of Censoring Weighted Methods for Survival Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Emily", "Zabor", email = "emily.zabor@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Anne", "Eaton", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides functions to implement inverse probability of censoring
    weighted (IPCW) methods for survival analysis, covering both single-event
    and competing-risks settings. Includes utilities for computing IPCW weights,
    fitting weighted Cox proportional hazards models, estimating weighted
    Kaplan-Meier survival curves, and computing weighted cumulative incidence
    functions under competing risks. Bootstrap variance estimation is also
    supported.
